# LogFlickScanner - Log Activity Analyzer

LogFlickScanner identifies repeated log entries, alert bursts, and clustered events that may indicate instability.

## Features
- Timestamp correlation  
- Pattern matching  
- Frequency breakdown  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/30_LogFlickScanner.git
cd 30_LogFlickScanner
python analyze.py /var/log/app.log
